# Delivered art drops (the pristine ~400 KB originals, straight from the illustrator).
# The build only needs the palette-quantized copies under public/assets/shutterbug-ui/,
# which ARE tracked; keeping the raw drop out saves ~30 MB per batch in the repo and in
# every clone. Trailing * so the next drop ("… assets 2") is caught too — 89bcd9f got
# 30 MB of these into history via a `git add -A` before this rule existed.
Shutterbug new image assets*/
art-drops/

# Natural Earth source data cached by scripts/gen-geography.mjs (hundreds of MB)
scripts/.cache/
